SKILLS REFERENCE
ANALYTICS TRACKING
EVENT_NAMING noun + verb (e.g., `button_clicked`, `form_submitted`). Consistent across ventures.
A/B TEST SETUP
One variable per test. Define the success metric before TT starts — no post-hoc interpretation. Minimum 2-week run or 500 conversions per variant — whichever comes first. Avoid: stopping a test early when results look promising — significance requires the full window. 
SAAS REVENUE GROWTH METRICS
TRACK MRR, ARR, MoM growth rate, NRR, CR, expansion MRR, contraction MRR.
BUSINESS HEALTH DIAGNOSTIC
Run all 4 quadrants: growth, retention, margin, cash. Flag any metric 20%+ below benchmark immediately — not at the end of the session. Avoid: presenting data without period-over-period context or benchmark comparison. 